about taking care of him,

24:41.729 --> 24:43.098
we do have a new offer.

24:43.131 --> 24:44.602
Of course you do.

24:44.635 --> 24:45.904
-For a nominal fee...
-Here he goes.

24:45.937 --> 24:47.273
