-No.

24:48.776 --> 24:50.312
[snarling]

24:50.345 --> 24:51.716
[Laszlo]
What the fuck?

24:51.749 --> 24:55.022
[guttural]
Who calls... Topher?

24:55.055 --> 24:56.659
What's this "Thriller" shit?

24:56.692 --> 24:59.297
-[gasping]
-[screaming]

24:59.330 --> 25:00.867
[normal voice]
JK.

25:00.900 --> 25:02.036
-[laughter]
-[Laszlo] Oh, it's that guy.

25:02.069 --> 25:04.274
-Topher!
-Yeah, baby. Sup, guys?

25:04.307 --> 25:05.911
How you doing, Guillermo?

25:05.944 --> 25:07.748
[Guillermo]
Topher, you look, uh...

25:07.781 --> 25:09.317
-You look like shit.
-Well, I'm au naturel, babe.

25:09.350 --> 25:11.021
I've had some work done.

25:11.054 --> 25:12.591
You know, I'm still undead,

25:12.624 --> 25:14.127
but I'm making
the most of it, man.

25:14.160 --> 25:15.997
Once you get used
to the zombie body,

25:16.030 --> 25:18.168
you can actually learn
to talk normal again.

25:18.201 --> 25:20.172
Like this. Pretty cool, huh?

25:20.205 --> 25:21.943
-He just does the accent
for the tourists.
-Eh, you know.

25:21.976 --> 25:23.680
Take 'em for an arm and a leg.

25:23.713 --> 25:25.282
-[laughter]
-Yeah, man.

25:25.315 --> 25:26.752
Who we got here?

25:26.785 --> 25:28.957
-Der. Ek.
-[Topher] Oh, hey, look at that.

25:28.990 --> 25:30.694
Yeah, he's trying.

25:30.727 --> 25:32.063
It's gonna take him
a couple months

25:32.096 --> 25:33.666
to learn how to use
the ol' mouth again.

25:33.699 --> 25:35.670
But in the meantime,
the more the merrier.

25:35.703 --> 25:38.142
Hey, Derek. How would you
like to join a gang

25:38.175 --> 25:40.212
of crazy motherfuckers
just like yourself?

25:40.245 --> 25:41.949
There's always room
for a new friend.

25:41.982 --> 25:44.354
-Friend?
-Yeah. Friend!

25:44.387 --> 25:46.091
High five! [laughs]

25:46.124 --> 25:47.895
Oh, yeah, takes a second.

25:47.928 --> 25:49.297
-Come on, buddy.
-Whoa!

25:49.330 --> 25:51.368
-Easy, Derek.
-[laughs]

25:51.401 --> 25:54.809
Hey, boys, set a place at the
table for our new friend Derek!

25:54.842 --> 25:56.344
-[zombies cheering]
-[laughter]

25:56.377 --> 25:58.115
Hey, you like eating
human flesh?

25:58.148 --> 26:00.654
-[growls]
-Oh, you will.

26:00.687 --> 26:02.056
Very... cool.

26:02.089 --> 26:04.394
-Bye, Derek.
-[Laszlo] Bye, Derek.

